product_title: 925 Sterling Silver Finish 6ct Simulated Diamond Stud Set
review_body:
Great product.. I got this set for my mother, as she is allergic to bijoux (probably to the nickel in some products, I don't know for sure, I just know that her ears get swallowed, red and itchy unless is silver or gold).
